Question 42. 
 
 
 
 
 
 
 
 
MSQ (1M)
Question ID : 8232513113
In the context of compilers, which of the following is/are NOT an intermediate representation of
the source program?
(A) 3 Address code 
 
(B) Symbol Table
(C) Control Flow Graph  
(D) Abstract Syntax Tree
explanation_text:
Sol. 
Symbol table is data structure used to store information related to variables, function name etc.
